Package Photos.Controller

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdminController
    Defines the functions of the admin subsystem, with this controller and admin.fxml.
    AlbumController
    Controller that handles the Album view, which displays the list of albums of the currently logged in user.
    Controller
    Abstract class that defines the functions for all the controllers in this application.
    LoginController
    Handles the login screen for the user.
    PhotoController
    Handles the photo view that shows when opening an album.
    SearchController
    Handles the Search action of the user.
